<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Start Selling on Thriftify!</title>
    <style>
        .head-con {
            width: 100%;
            height: 50px;
            background-color: green;
            color: white;
            font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
        }
        body {
            font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        section {
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        p {
            line-height: 1.6;
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #333;
        }
       
        .cta-button:hover {
            background-color: darkgreen;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <div class="head-con">
            <h2 class="head">Thriftify</h2>
        </div>
    </header>
    <section>
        <h2>Hello {{name}},</h2>
        <p>
            We noticed that you've successfully verified your account, but you haven't listed any items yet!
        </p>
        <p>
            Thriftiffy is a great place to sell your second-hand items and make extra cash. Don't miss out on potential buyers waiting for your listings.
        </p>
        <p>
            Click the button below to list your first item and start selling today:
        </p>
        <p>
            <a href="{{link}}"  target="_blank">List Your First Item</a>
        </p>
        <p>
            If you need any help, feel free to contact our support team.
        </p>
        <p>
            Best regards,<br />
            The Thriftiffy Team
        </p>
    </section>
</body>
</html>
